reviewText: This is a short CD, yes interesting and a bit entertaining, yet I was disappointed and gave this one away.

I'm looking for this Behind the scenes so long and whenever I found it, I coudn't believe it!
So happy that I get it!

There is nothing that Celine does in Concert that she doeswn't do Top Drawer!! Any concert...any purchase is money well spent and many hours of enjoyable entertainment. I play mine DVD's & Tape over & over!
